    <content type="html">
      &lt;pre style=&#39;white-space:pre-wrap;width:81ex&#39;&gt;Enhance context acquisition on chart creation

Add support for creating a chart from the canvas id and prevent exceptions, at construction time, when the given item doesn&amp;#39;t provide a valid CanvasRenderingContext2D or when the getContext API is not accessible (e.g. undefined by add-ons to prevent fingerprinting). New jasmine matcher to verify chart validity.&lt;/pre&gt;
    </content>
